        "Discription": "Participants learn core Python concepts such as data types, loops, and functions, along with advanced topics like object-oriented programming and handling exceptions. The course covers popular Python frameworks such as Django and Flask for web development, as well as libraries like NumPy and Pandas for data manipulation and analysis. By the end of this course, you will have gained a strong foundation in Python programming and will be capable ofbuilding software applications, performing data analysis, and working on web development projects. Python is aversatile and widely used language in various fields, and this course will empower you with the skills needed to excel in the world of programming and development.",
